plot_nonviol <- dat %>%
  filter(is.finite(avg_temp), is.finite(alcohol_drive_cases+theft_cases+general_injury_cases+drug_cases+sexual_assault_cases)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = avg_temp, y = alcohol_drive_cases+theft_cases+general_injury_cases+drug_cases+sexual_assault_cases)) +
  geom_point(alpha = .3, na.rm = TRUE) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, se = TRUE, na.rm = TRUE) +
  labs(title = "Non-violent vs Temperature",
       x = "Avg Temp (°C)", y = "Non-violent cases")
plot_nonviol

coef_nonviol <- tidy(m_nonviol_fe) %>% mutate(model = "Non-violent crimes")
coef_viol    <- tidy(m_viol_fe)    %>% mutate(model = "Violent crimes")

coef_nonviol_plot <- coef_nonviol %>%
  filter(term %in% c("avg_temp", "rainy_days", "sunshine_hours", "avg_humidity")) %>%
  mutate(term = recode(term,
                       avg_temp = "Average Temperature",
                       rainy_days = "Rainy Days",
                       sunshine_hours = "Sunshine Hours",
                       avg_humidity = "Average Humidity"))

coef_viol_plot <- coef_viol %>%
  filter(term %in% c("avg_temp", "rainy_days", "sunshine_hours", "avg_humidity")) %>%
  mutate(term = recode(term,
                       avg_temp = "Average Temperature",
                       rainy_days = "Rainy Days",
                       sunshine_hours = "Sunshine Hours",
                       avg_humidity = "Average Humidity"))
library(patchwork)  # 安裝：install.packages("patchwork")

library(patchwork)

p1 <- ggplot(coef_nonviol_plot, aes(x = term, y = estimate, fill = term)) +
  geom_col(width = 0.6) +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = estimate - 1.96*std.error,
                    ymax = estimate + 1.96*std.error),
                width = 0.15) +
  labs(title = "Non-violent Crimes",
       x = "Climate Variables",
       y = "Regression Coefficient (±95% CI)") +
  theme_minimal(base_family = "ch", base_size = 14) +
  theme(legend.position = "none")

p2 <- ggplot(coef_viol_plot, aes(x = term, y = estimate, fill = term)) +
  geom_col(width = 0.6) +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = estimate - 1.96*std.error,
                    ymax = estimate + 1.96*std.error),
                width = 0.15) +
  labs(title = "Violent Crimes",
       x = "Climate Variables",
       y = "Regression Coefficient (±95% CI)") +
  theme_minimal(base_family = "ch", base_size = 14) +
  theme(legend.position = "none")

p1 / p2 + plot_annotation(title = "Comparative Effects of Climate Variables on Crime Types")
